title: Joomla-Builder-installation-with-templates-and-extensions
description:
Full-featured extended Joomla CMS installation generated by Joomla-Builder.Com.
It contains all kinds of Joomla extensions already pre-installed.
Includes free Forum, Gallery, online shop (VirtueMart). Contains a lot of other useful Joomla extensions and Joomla templates. Useful stuff for webmaster.
A portal system ready for deployment on hosting, no knowledge of PHP is necessary, good for beginners.
